

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/SignUp.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; padding-top: 20px">
        <a><img height="150" width="175" src=" /images/PrimeMarket_Logo.png" alt="PrimeMarket Logo" /></a>
    </div>
    <br />
    <h2>Sign Up</h2>
    <form asp-action="SignUp" asp-controller="User" method="post">
        <div style="
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 150px;
    margin-top: 50px;
  ">
            <!-- First div -->
            <div>
                <p>Name & Last Name</p>
                <input style="
                padding: 8px 16px;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 20px;
                width: 250px;
                outline: none;
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
              " type="text" id="username" name="username" required placeholder="Enter your name & last name">
                <br>
                <br>
                <p>Email</p>
                <input style="
                padding: 8px 16px;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 20px;
                width: 250px;
                outline: none;
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
              " type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="Enter an email">
                <br>
                <br>
                <p>Password</p>
                <input style="
                padding: 8px 16px;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 20px;
                width: 250px;
                outline: none;
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
              " type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="Enter a password">
                <br>
                <br>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
                    <button style="
          cursor: pointer;
          padding: 8px 16px;
          border: 1px solid #ddd;
          border-radius: 20px;
        " type="submit" id="signup-btn" disabled>
                        Sign Up
                    </button>
                </div>
                <br />
                <p>Already have an account?<a asp-action="Login" asp-controller="User"> Login</a></p>
            </div>

            <!-- Second div -->
            <div>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Terms Of Conditions For PrimeMarket</p>
                <br>
                <div class="terms-box" style="border-radius:20px; padding:10px; width:120%">
                    <pre>
    Terms and Conditions 
    (That You Won’t Read Anyway)
    Welcome to our app/website! By 
    using this service, you 
    agree to the following terms — not 
    that you’ll read them, 
    but hey, legal stuff, right?

    Acceptance of Terms
    By scrolling, clicking, or 
    even accidentally 
    touching your screen, 
    you agree to everything 
    written here, even the parts 
    that sound ridiculous.

    Data Collection
    We promise to collect only 
    the data we need... and also 
    the data 
    we don't need, just in case. 
    This includes your 
    location, favorite snacks, 
    and how long you stared 
    at that one product before 
    eciding not to buy it.

    User Responsibilities
    You’re responsible for everything. 
    Yes, everything. 
    If your cat walks on your 
    keyboard and accidentally 
    orders a lifetime supply of 
    glitter, that’s on you.

    Service Availability
